snippet.title: Cube Escape: The Lake Trailer [Rusty Lake]
snippet.description:
Promo for Cube Escape: The Lake!

You've found an abandoned cabin on a small Island at Rusty Lake. The only thing you can find is some fishing gear, a knive and a crow bar.

Download now for iOS (Iphone and Ipad):
https://itunes.apple.com/app/id983081008
Download on Android:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.RustyLake.CubeEscapeTheLake 
Or play on web:
http://www.rustylake.com/room-escape-games/cube-escape-the-lake.html

Play more Cube Escape games at RustyLake.com!
